No. 94,

Orig.

South Carolina v. Baker, Secretary of the Treasury. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 469 U. S. 1083.]

Report of the Special Master is received and ordered filed. Exceptions to the Report, with supporting briefs, may be filed by the parties within 45 days. Replies thereto, with supporting briefs, may be filed within 30 days.
